芝加哥干草叉音乐节 19 年后取消https://www.nme.com/news/music/pitchfork-festival-in-chicago-cancelled-after-19-years-3811687?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pitchfork-festival-in-chicago-cancelled-after- 19岁Emma WilkesMon, 11 Nov 2024 20:12:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3811687 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们期待继续创造音乐、文化和社区以令人振奋的方式交汇的空间”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pitchfork-festival-in-chicago-cancelled-after-19-years-3811687">芝加哥 Pitchfork 音乐节在 19 年后被取消，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Pitchfork 一年一度的芝加哥音乐节在运营 19 年后，将不会在 2025 年举行。</p><p>该媒体在 Instagram 上发表官方声明，证实这项长期举办的活动明年不会回归，理由是当前音乐节格局正在迅速变化。</p><p>声明中写道：“这个决定并不是轻易做出的。” “19 年来，Pitchfork 音乐节一直是音乐、艺术和社区的庆典——一个创造回忆、放大声音、对音乐的共同热爱将我们聚集在一起的空间。</p><p> “这个节日虽然符合 Pitchfork 编辑团队的品味，但始终是一项协作努力，作为芝加哥艺术界的重要支柱，它拥有自己的生命力。我们深深感谢芝加哥市近二十年来一直作为我们音乐节的举办地，感谢那些以令人难忘的表演为我们的舞台增光添彩的艺术家，感谢年复一年为我们带来无与伦比能量的粉丝。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCPeBMKJxWA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 